articles.title: Eminem, The Killers, Muse lead lineup for Bonnaroo Festival
articles.description: NASHVILLE (AP) — Eminem, The Killers, Muse, Future, Bassnectar and Sturgill Simpson lead the lineup for this year’s Bonnaroo Music and Arts Festival.
